<h3>AOD-9604 vs. Full HGH: Side-by-Side</h3>

<table class="tbl">
<thead><tr><th>Effect</th><th>Full HGH</th><th>AOD-9604</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td><strong>Fat breakdown</strong></td><td class="g">Yes</td><td class="g">Yes</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>IGF-1 elevation</strong></td><td class="r">Yes</td><td class="g">No</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Blood sugar increase</strong></td><td class="r">Yes</td><td class="g">No</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Bone/cartilage growth</strong></td><td class="r">Yes</td><td class="g">No</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Organ enlargement</strong></td><td class="r">Yes</td><td class="g">No</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Water retention</strong></td><td class="r">Yes</td><td class="g">No</td></tr>
